<!-- PROJECT -->
<section>
<h2>Featured Project</h2>

<div class="project">
<h3>Omnichannel Retail Performance Analysis</h3>

<p><strong>Project Overview:</strong><br>
This project focuses on analyzing retail business performance across customers, products,
and pricing strategies using Power BI. The objective was to convert raw operational data
into structured insights that enhance strategic decision-making.
</p>

<p><strong>Dashboard Structure:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Overview Dashboard – High-level KPIs and performance tracking</li>
<li>Customer Analysis – Segmentation, behavior & profitability</li>
<li>Product Analysis – Pricing gaps and category performance</li>
</ul>

<p><strong>Key Features:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Interactive dashboards with filters & drill-down capabilities</li>
<li>Advanced tooltip pages for contextual insights</li>
<li>Dynamic insight generation based on user interaction</li>
<li>Profit & margin analysis using MSRP vs Standard Cost</li>
</ul>

<p><strong>Technical Implementation:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Star schema data modeling</li>
<li>DAX measures for Profit, Margin, AOV</li>
<li>Conditional formatting & performance optimization</li>
<li>Scatter plot pricing strategy evaluation</li>
</ul>

<p><strong>Business Insights:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>High-value customer segments drive the majority of profits</li>
<li>Some high-revenue products yield low profitability</li>
<li>Pricing variations reveal margin improvement opportunities</li>
<li>Performance varies significantly across categories</li>
</ul>

<p>
This project demonstrates the ability to integrate analytical thinking
with advanced visualization techniques to deliver business-focused intelligence solutions.
</p>

